title: Uncanny X-Force 2010-2012 (complete)
description:
This is a request by a member here.  While I am more able to provide current issues, IF I can find what you are looking for I will try and post it for you.  Nemesis43 on KAT has far more resources than I and is a better bet, but I will do what I can to help the communities.  Please message me privatly for requests so as not to clutter up comment sections with unrelated material.









Uncanny X-Force was a comic book ongoing series published by Marvel Comics. Created by writer Rick Remender and artist Jerome OpeÃƒÂ±a, the first volume of the series continued the story of Wolverine and his X-Force team from the series X-Force, vol. 3.[1] The title was relaunched after issue #35 as part of the Marvel NOW! relaunch event, and the new volume feature Psylocke and Storm leading a new team of "outcasts and scoundrels".[2]

The series was one of two X-Force ongoing titles, along with Cable and X-Force.
